{"tid":235312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【舉國痛心】重男輕女敍爸咬死B女 小小身驅滿咬痕","createTime":"2017-05-09T02:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T02:25:13.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbe422149ed68e8e691d1cc2581e915be9e93bd","tid":235312,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170508/large/1494234886_b35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170508%2Flarge%2F1494234886_b35a.jpg&h=a431a08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在父母眼中子女理應最可愛，但敘利亞一名喪盡天良的狠父竟認為女兒是恥辱的根源，將9個月大女兒活生生咬死，女嬰死時身上傷痕纍纍，令看慣戰火無情的敍利亞人也非常憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n9個月大女童達拉（Dalal）樣子討人喜愛，但她的37歲父親極度重男輕女，視女性為恥辱。上月24日，達拉母親稱早已發現丈夫不妥，擔心他威脅女兒安全，急忙向鄰居求助，但她回家時女兒已經傷痕纍纍。相片可見，達拉臉上有大片瘀傷，身上亦有不少咬痕，她送院後不治，醫院證實她被虐死。<br />\n不少敘利亞人對事件表示痛心疾首，又指戰亂和家暴為當地人留下巨大陰影，「沒有死於子彈下的人，也會死於神經錯亂」。<br />\n敍利亞當局非常關注事件，安全部隊及檢察機關也介入事件，目前達拉父母均被捕。"},{"pid":"bc93241db0ffe4f435381adf77709f9defe858da","tid":235312,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"屌死刑啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e49da4abfd6bf05f1afe8e5bbfddaf4b530cdcb","tid":235312,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"係敘利亞仲生咩細路...."},{"pid":"7a36cddecde2db0c637e51240e562159ba37b585","tid":235312,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係敘利亞仲生咩細路....</blockquote><br />\n避孕會真主皇天擊殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11350c9ade0d5a6372b9e80f8556f7fd030e2cc1","tid":235312,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"